In the Army Now;;1994;;PG;;Comedy,War;;5.0;;Daniel Petrie Jr.;;Pauly Shore,Lori Petty,Andy Dick,David Alan Grier,Esai Morales,Lynn Whitfield,Art LaFleur,Fabiana Udenio,Glenn Morshower,Beau Billingslea,Peter Spellos,Barry Nolan,Coleen Christie,Ryan Cutrona,Paul Mooney,Richard Assad,Allen R. Stokes,Earl M. Nicholson;;Bones and Jack are two guys with very little going right in their lives. The two decide to join the Army as part of the water purification team and eventually find themselves on the front lines in the conflict between the northern African countries of Chad and Libya. The two men, along with a few companions, have it upon themselves to save the day in combat, something they know little about.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0110123/